Package: gity
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Fast Git helper daemon for large repositories
 Gity is a background daemon that accelerates Git operations for large
 repositories by maintaining warm caches, scheduling maintenance tasks,
 and providing instant status queries.
 .
 Features:
  - Filesystem monitoring for tracked repositories
  - Background prefetch and maintenance scheduling
  - Fast cached status queries via fsmonitor protocol
  - Optional system tray UI
